{"type":null,"faqId":48033,"title":"拍摄模式","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n.s2{font-weight:bold;}\n.s3{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.41527778in;}\n.p1{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{text-indent:-0.110416666in;margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p5{text-indent:1.0979167in;margin-left:0.072916664in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p6{text-indent:0.072916664in;margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p7{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n.p8{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n.p9{text-indent:1.3173611in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p10{margin-left:1.15625in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n <span>. “美妆”：通过设置不同的特效处理模式，精准定位人像面部器官并进行特效处理，轻松拍出精致容颜。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>“美肤”：通过拖动滑块调节美肤级别，美化人像面部肌肤，让照片中的您看上去更美丽动人。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>“全景”：可拍摄更为宽广的照片。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>“HDR”：可改善光线不足或光线过亮时的拍照效果。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>“全焦”：可首先完成拍照，随后在图库中重新选择对焦点。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>“连拍选优”：手机可在连拍数张后，选出效果最佳的照片。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>“水印”：为拍摄的照片添加各种水印图案。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>“在线翻译”：对准目标文字，可联网翻译为指定语言。该功能需连接网络。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>“智能识物”：相机拍照后，从照片中选择对象，进行联网识别。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>“有声照片”：可在拍照的同时录制几秒钟音频，记录下当时的声音。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>“美食”：通过调节色调和光线，拍出让您垂涎欲滴的美食。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>“声控拍照”：点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177915\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”，在“设置”中启用本功能。启用后，可发出口令，进行拍照。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>“定时拍照”：点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177916\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”，在“设置”中启用并设定定时拍照的时间。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>“触摸拍照”：点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177917\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”，在“设置”中启用本功能。启用后，可以触摸取景界面进行拍照。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>“笑脸抓拍”：点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177918\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”，在“设置”中启用本功能。启用后，相机检测到笑脸时可自动拍照。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>“目标跟踪”：点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177919\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”，在“设置”中启用本功能。启用后，选定一个拍摄对象后，手机将始终以该对象为对焦点进行拍摄。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>“熄屏快拍”：点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177920\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”，在“设置”中启用本功能。启用后，在屏幕关闭或锁屏状态下，对准要拍摄的对象，连续两次按下音量下键，相机自动拍摄。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">拍摄全景照片</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"拍摄全景照片\"XE \"切换全景拍照方向\"XE \"全景\"XE \"调整全景拍照方向\"</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s3\">1.  </span><span>在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177921\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“相机”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s3\">2.  </span><span>点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177922\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span> &gt; 全景”，切换到全景模式。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s3\">3.  </span><span>点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177923\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”，开始拍摄。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s3\">4.  </span><span>按照屏幕提示缓慢平稳地移动或小幅度旋转手机，拍下多组连续画面。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s3\">5.  </span><span>点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177924\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”停止拍摄。相机自动将拍摄的多组画面合成全景照片。</span><a name=\"_task_take_best_photo-chtext\"></a>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s2\">使用连拍选优</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"使用连拍选优\"XE \"挑选连拍照片\"XE \"连拍选优\"XE \"连续拍摄照片\"XE \"连拍照片\"</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>1.在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177925\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“相机”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>2.点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177926\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span> &gt; 连拍选优”，切换到连拍选优模式。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>3.点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177927\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”拍摄照片。手机会在一系列连拍照片中自动选择一张最佳照片。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>4.点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177928\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>您可以继续选择其他照片，手机将自动保存选中的照片并删除剩余照片。</span><a name=\"_task_take_watermark_photo-chtext\"></a>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">拍摄水印照片</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"拍摄水印照片\"XE \"为照片添加水印\"XE \"添加照片水印\"XE \"水印\"XE \"水印照片\"XE \"照片水印\"</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>1.在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177929\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“相机”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>2.点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177930\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span> &gt; 水印”，切换到水印模式。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>3.左右滑动屏幕，选择要添加的水印。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>4.在屏幕上拖动水印，调整水印在照片中的位置。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>5.点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177931\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”。</span><a name=\"_task_use_voicecontrol-chtext\"></a>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span class=\"s2\">使用声控拍照</span><span>XE \"使用声控拍照\"XE \"声控拍摄照片\"XE \"声音控制拍照\"</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>1.在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177932\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“相机”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>2.点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177933\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span> &gt; </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177934\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span> &gt; 声控拍照”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>3.点击“声控拍照”开关，开启声控拍照模式，您可以：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>设置手机在听到预设口令时自动拍照。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>设置手机在周边声音达到一定大小时自动拍照。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span>4.将镜头对准要拍摄的对象。当手机听到预设命令，或者周边声音达到一定强度时，手机将自动拍照。</span><a name=\"_task_use_object_tracking-chtext\"></a>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<span class=\"s2\">使用目标跟踪</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"使用目标跟踪\"XE \"使用追随拍照\"XE \"开启跟踪拍照\"XE \"目标跟踪\"XE \"实时对焦\"XE \"跟踪对焦\"</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span>1.在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177935\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“相机”。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span>2.点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177936\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span> &gt; </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177937\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span>3.点击“目标跟踪”开关，开启目标跟踪模式。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span>4.在拍照界面点击一个拍摄对象，相机将始终以该对象为对焦点进行拍摄。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p7\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177938\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p8\">\n<span>目标跟踪与笑脸抓拍功能无法同时开启。</span><a name=\"_task_on_focus-chtext\"></a>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p9\">\n<span class=\"s2\">全焦模式</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"全焦\"XE \"先拍照\"XE \"后对焦\"XE \"焦距\"XE \"变焦\"XE \"焦点\"XE \"全焦模式\"XE \"改变焦点\"</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span>1.在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177939\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“相机”。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span>2.点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177940\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span> &gt; 全焦”，切换到全焦模式。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span>3.点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177941\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”拍摄照片。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span>4.在图库中，选择全焦模式下拍摄的照片。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p7\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177942\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p8\">\n<span>在全焦模式下拍摄的照片会显示图标“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177943\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span>5.点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177944\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”，进入全焦编辑状态。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span>6.点击要清晰显示的地方，将其设为焦点。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span>7.点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177945\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p10\"></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":1086,"faqType":"相机与图库","useful":4,"unUseful":4,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"3619","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Camera-Gallery","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1445598096000,"seriesProductName":"RIO-AL00,RIO-CL00,RIO-TL00,RIO-UL00,RIO-UL10","visitedTimes":99,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":3,"times":1,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":3.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}